261
00:19:15.840 --> 00:19:18.510
Pound! Pound! Pound!
Pound! Pound! Pound!

262
00:19:22.590 --> 00:19:25.220
Damn, you're all over the place!

263
00:19:25.220 --> 00:19:28.940
Ha! Ba! You ba! What's the point...

264
